public class ServerActivity
extends android.support.v4.app.FragmentActivity

UI class for the server-based data browsing feature (OpenSensor Server). Extends the Android support compatibility library's FragmentActivity instead of Activity in order to utilize the date-picker Fragment feature. It also includes objects for managing query-building (ServerSearchQueryBuilder) and geocoding (SimpleGeocoder).

Author:
Nikos Moumoulidis
